node.text:
Are you afraid of heights?😵‍💫

I am comfortable on cliffs like this 90% of the time…. and the other 10% I get a funny/uneasy feeling in my gut and immediately step away from the spot I’m in😬 Here’s a reminder no one asked for—don’t do anything you’re not comfortable doing. Safety first, pals! No photo is worth it. 

Photo shot by @chrisrlocke

node.text:
If you could go somewhere right now, where would it be?✈️

When traveling, it’s incredibly important to get travel insurance. @battleface_plan offers reliable protection and was created with the traveler in mind. They understand that your plans may change and make it easy to stay safe when you’re on an adventure—wherever that may be🌍

Why @battleface_plan?
① Optional cancel for any reason coverage
② Customizable insurance to fit your travel needs (buy just what you need, doesn’t need to be “full coverage”)
③ COVID Coverage
④ Easy to use app⁣

Pop on their website to get a quote♥️

#battleface #ad #travelinsurance

node.text:
Wildflowers, alpine lakes and endless trails to explore—this is summer in BC. Oh, also bears and mosquitos😜

It is common to see grizzlies in this meadow so I made sure I gathered a lot of friends (there was an unreal group of 7 of us), we made noise, looked around and had what we needed in the case of an emergency (bear spray & satellite phone). 

If you get nervous about bears like me remember that if you do the things in order to prevent an encounter (make noise, look around/don’t surprise a bear, etc) then you’ve done all you can do! Also, remember that moooost bears are just doing their thing and won’t attack you for just the thrill of it.

Photo shot by @coastalkells

node.text:
New Zealand♥️🇳🇿 A country that feels like home and holds a special place in my heart. 

Conversations are happening about reopening the country to fully vaxxed travellers by next year and I can’t freakin’ wait.

If you didn’t know, I’m hosting a group trip to NZ in November 2022. There are a few spots open so if you want something to look forward to, head to the link in my bio for more info and DM me if you wanna chat about it😌✈️

Photo by @brendinkelly
